Package com.oracle.coherence.concurrent.executor

Class RecoveringTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oracle.coherence.concurrent.executor.RecoveringTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Task<Boolean>, ExternalizableLite, PortableObject, Serializable
    public class RecoveringTask
extends Object
implements Task<Boolean>, PortableObject
    A Task that runs for at least a specified Duration, returning the resuming / recovering status when completed.

    21.12
